				"{image:firstaid:item/bandage width:25 height:25 align:center}"
				"&lPlaster&r"
				"{image:firstaid:item/plaster width:25 height:25 align:center}"
				"&lMedical Kit&r"
				"{image:superbwarfare:item/medical_kit width:25 height:25 align:center}"
				""
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"Some medical supplies can only be obtained by mob drops."
