		{
			dependencies: ["3582892076B0AD1A"]
			description: [
				"You must have full hyderation and no hunger in order to heal naturally. You can drink water, but drinking non-purified water may"
				"give you thirst status effect."
				""
				"&l&4Thirst&r&r"
				"{image:toughasnails:textures/mob_effect/thirst.png width:25 height:25 align:center}"
				""
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"You can find purified water in the city, as well as craft it using a"
				"water purifier."
				""
				"&lWater Purifier&r"
				"{image:toughasnails:block/water_purifier_front width:25 height:25 align:center}"
				""
				"It requires burning &lCharcoal&r"
				"{image:minecraft:item/charcoal width:25 height:25 align:center}"
				""
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"You can use canteens to store lots of water and purify together."
				""
				"&lLeather Canteen&r"
				"{image:toughasnails:item/empty_leather_canteen width:25 height:25 align:center}"
				""
				"You can upgrade all the way to &lNetherite Canteen&r"
				"{image:toughasnails:item/netherite_purified_water_canteen width:25 height:25 align:center}"
			]
