		{
			dependencies: ["3582892076B0AD1A"]
			description: [
				"You are affected by the temperature of your surrounding biome and objects. You may freeze to death if you get too cold and burn to death if you get too hot."
				""
				"Use a thermoregulator to balance out the surrounding temperature, this will allow you to stay at room temperature without needing the necessary armor. "
				""
				"&lThermoregulator&r"
				"{image:toughasnails:block/thermoregulator_front_active width:25 height:25 align:center}"
				""
				"It needs ice, packed ice, or blue ice as fuel for cooling."
				"{image:minecraft:block/blue_ice width:25 height:25 align:center}"
				""
				"It needs coal, coal blocks, or a lava bucket for heating."
				"{image:minecraft:item/coal width:25 height:25 align:center}"
				""
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"Armor set to survive the &l&4heat&r&r. Made of leaves"
				"{image:toughasnails:item/leaf_helmet width:25 height:25 align:center}"
				"{image:toughasnails:item/leaf_chestplate width:25 height:25 align:center}"
				"{image:toughasnails:item/leaf_leggings width:25 height:25 align:center}"
				"{image:toughasnails:item/leaf_boots width:25 height:25 align:center}"
				""
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"Armor set to survive the &l&1cold&r&r. Made of wool"
				"{image:toughasnails:item/wool_helmet width:25 height:25 align:center}"
				"{image:toughasnails:item/wool_chestplate width:25 height:25 align:center}"
				"{image:toughasnails:item/wool_leggings width:25 height:25 align:center}"
				"{image:toughasnails:item/wool_boots width:25 height:25 align:center}"
				""
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"You can build an insulation charm that protects you from all extreme temperature damage without needing any armor or a thermoregulator."
				""
				"&e&lUniversal&r&r Thermal Body Insulation"
				"{image:tan__a_curios_expansion:item/universalthermalinsulation width:25 height:25 align:center}"
				""
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"You can use the calender to monitor the season. The season effects the temperature world wide, as well as impacting farming."
				""
				"&l&5Calender&r&r"
				"{image:sereneseasons:item/calendar_00 width:25 height:25 align:center}"
